Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.57,0:01:28.06,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}然而
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:33.35,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}Mr.teacher請告訴不成熟的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.39,0:01:38.85,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}何時才能擊倒你這個不落的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.06,0:01:44.35,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}只要挑戰 可能性是half＆half
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:49.34,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}Mr.teacher請看著迷茫的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:54.59,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}為了你比任何人都認真學習
